        <abstract> 
<p>At work on <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Discusses John Ball’s, G. de Saporta’s, and his own theories of higher plant origin. Their rapid development remains an "abominable mystery".</p>
            <p>Frank is working in Würzburg.</p>
        </abstract>
